data.description: Move in Ready Home is Up For Sale near the schools in Canyon, Texas. This 3 BR 1.5 BA home features a nice layout, 1 car garage, big fenced in backyard and lots of extras including all appliances and washer dryer. If you're thinking about investing, this is ready to rent out tonight! Clean as a whistle with all new locks, newer roof, HVAC and water heater less than a year old per the seller. Come home to Canyon!
